snippet: Maria Sharapova and Victoria Azarenka, who will meet in the French Open semifinals, have reputations not only as powerful ball-strikers but also as the game’s most high-pitched shriekers.
abstract: Maria Sharapova and Victoria Azarenka, both of whom have reputations not only as powerful ball-strikers but also as tennis' most high-pitched shriekers, are set to meet in the French Open semifinals.
lead_paragraph: Maria Sharapova and Victoria Azarenka, who will meet in the French Open semifinals, have reputations not only as powerful ball-strikers but also as the game’s most high-pitched shriekers.
